data.description:
Seller willing to replace Roof!!!
Excellent Townhome with many upgrades. First off, there is an Enclosed Garage that gives a 4th bedroom/office or hobby room. Updated Kitchen, high ceilings and nice floors throughout. One of the BEST FEATURES is the Enclosed Florida Glassed Room with stamped concrete!!! Townhome is at the end of a cul de sac with extra parking. This is a Great Location in the growing area of Jacksonville's Southside. Very close to St. John's Town Center thats only minutes away, also very central for a quick trip to the Beaches, Airport, and Downtown.
Don't miss out on the Townhome. Low HOA Fees.
